data.description: Discover this welcoming 3 bedroom, 2 bath home brimming with untapped potential! With a little TLC, you'll turn this home into the one you've been envisioning! Enjoy ample main level space-including  a bedroom and full bath, versatile family room, formal dining room, and spacious living room. Step through the sliding glass doors to access a deck, a enclosed yard, and an extra detached garage.  Upstairs you'll find two additional bedrooms and a 1/2 bath. This home is ready for your personal touch. Contact us to see its possibilities!
